NOTE:
Plants with a total steam-electric nameplate capacity of 10 MW or greater are required to report the configuration of their environmental equipment.  (These plants are designated as Steam Plant Types 1comma 2comma or 3).  Some plants that are not Steam Plant Type 1comma 2comma or 3 have voluntarily reported the configuration of their environmental equipment; this voluntarily reported information is also displayed.
